snippet.title: Strätos for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

Strätos is an action game.

You have to defend the city from incoming alien attacks and meteor showers.

The city has a shield which makes it somewhat easier to defend it.


What I think:

Fun, but rather repetitive and not an easy game at all.
